<p><strong>Caesar Incident Update:</strong></p>
<blockquote>
<div class="scp-image-block block-right" style="width:300px; margin-top: 1.2em;"><img src="http://scp-wiki.wdfiles.com/local--files/captain-kirby-s-proposal/Site01Map.png" style="width:300px;" alt="Site01Map.png" class="image" />
